<section class="section section--no-border" style="padding-top:64px;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head section-head--center" style="max-width:640px;">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center;">FAQ</p>
      <h2>Your questions, <span class="accent">answered by us.</span></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-layout">
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false"><span>Who can apply?</span><span class="faq-item__icon"></span></button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><div class="faq-item__a-inner">If you're interested in research and are obsessed with solving hard problems &mdash; this is for you. We accept students from around the world.</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false"><span>Is the fellowship online?</span><span class="faq-item__icon"></span></button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><div class="faq-item__a-inner">Yes, the fellowship is completed 100% online and travel is not a part of this program.</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false"><span>Is financial assistance available?</span><span class="faq-item__icon"></span></button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><div class="faq-item__a-inner">Yes, we offer flexible payment plans to pay tuition over several months, and we award partial and full scholarships based on need and application quality.<br><br>Regardless of your financial situation, you should still apply! Learn more about tuition at aspireresearch.net/tuition.</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false"><span>Do I need research experience to apply?</span><span class="faq-item__icon"></span></button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><div class="faq-item__a-inner">No, but any form of rigorous scientific inquiry or a concrete demonstration of interest and execution is preferred.</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false"><span>Is publication guaranteed?</span><span class="faq-item__icon"></span></button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><div class="faq-item__a-inner">NO. Publication is not a guaranteed outcome for any program, as it is dependent on the quality of research among many other factors.</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false"><span>Is this only for STEM students?</span><span class="faq-item__icon"></span></button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><div class="faq-item__a-inner">Absolutely not. Research is a broad field, and our mentor network covers topics from literature to history and beyond!</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-cta">
        <span class="squiggle squiggle--drift" aria-hidden="true" style="width:90px; height:90px; left:-10px; top:-10px;">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 80 80"><path d="M40 70c-16 0-28-12-28-26 0-11 9-20 20-20 9 0 16 7 16 16 0 7-6 13-13 13-6 0-10-4-10-10 0-5 4-8 8-8"/></svg>
        </span>
        <img src="/assets/images/mentors/mentor-06.jpg" alt="" class="faq-cta__avatar">
        <h3>Still have questions?</h3>
        <a href="{{ nav.discordUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--dark btn--block">Ask us on Discord</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

